name: Jason Vorhees - friday the 13th
description:
This is the second artwork of the brazilian artist MACA, who puts together 3d art and music to represent pop figures. The second  figure is Jason one of the scariests figures of the pop culture, now as a NFT. Buy this NFT to enter into the MACA 3D POP world.

1, 2 He is coming for you.
